Therefore $i \points 2 \points n$ in $Q^{(2k+n-2)}$ and we compute:
\begin{align*}
b_{in}(Q^{(2k+n-1)}) - b_{in}(Q^{(2k+n-2)}) &=b_{i2}(Q^{(2k+n-2)}) b_{2n}(Q^{(2k+n-2)}) \\
