Proposition~\ref{pr:acyclic-mutation-cycle} shows that any $n$-vertex acyclic quiver~$Q$ lies on a mutation cycle of length~$n$
consisting entirely of acyclic quivers. 
All of them are re-orientations~of~$Q$. 

