\begin{proof}
%We argue by descending induction on~$j$. 
In the case $j=2k$, the claim
$Q^{(2k+n-2)}|_{12n}=Q^{(2k+1)}|_{12n}$ holds by Lemma~\ref{lem:Subquiver12nBottom}. %and then do regular induction on \ell. 
